    <item>
      <title>嘉能可迎来交易利润又一个强劲的一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/glencore-sees-yet-another-strong-year-for-trading-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可预计将迎来又一个丰收的贸易利润年，由于该交易商兼矿业公司从强劲的大宗商品价格和高利率中获利，目前有望达到其指导范围的顶部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/glencore-sees-yet-another-strong-year-for-trading-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 06:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着第一季度亏损扩大，法航-荷航希望削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/air-france-klm-looks-to-cut-costs-as-first-quarter-loss-widens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法航荷航集团报告称，由于费用增加、中东冲突和货运单位收入下降，导致第一季度运营亏损扩大，该公司将冻结招聘支持人员，作为削减成本的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/air-france-klm-looks-to-cut-costs-as-first-quarter-loss-widens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 06:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
