      <title>随着市场重新开放，日本股市因强劲盈利而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/japanese-stocks-face-surge-in-yen-volatility-as-market-reopens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一假期后，日本股市上涨，主要公司发布了强劲的企业财报。日立是东证指数中涨幅最大的股票之一，其涨幅为两个多月以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/japanese-stocks-face-surge-in-yen-volatility-as-market-reopens</guid>
